{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二回\"杀手\"紧接前章。杜青莲中毒倒下，挣扎着喝完最后一壶酒后坠入坑中身亡。邱凤城与马如龙对峙，邱凤城怀疑马如龙在酒中下毒以独占碧玉夫人女婿之位。马如龙冷漠应对，既不承认也不否认。金振林持金枪出现，要与邱凤城算旧账，二人激战之际，黑衣刺客突袭邱凤城。金振林趁机刺中邱凤城，但邱凤城因贴身藏着情人小婉所赠玉佩而幸免于死。金振林追击黑衣人时反被灭口。彭天霸、冯超凡、绝大师三人因追踪聚丰楼堂倌被杀之事来到寒梅谷，彭天霸一刀击毙黑衣人。邱凤城揭露阴谋：有人在酒中下毒害死杜青莲和沈红叶，又安排金振林和刺客伏击，意图独占碧玉山庄女婿之位，幕后黑手指向马如龙。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好酒，好酒。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_qing_lian",
      "speaker_name": "杜青莲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么好的酒，就算我明知有毒，也要喝的，你们看，我现在是不是已经喝下去了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你真的从来都不喝酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我知道你喝酒的，我也看过你喝酒，喝得还不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不但喝酒，而且常喝，常醉，有一次在杭州的珍珠坊，你日夜不停的连喝了三天，把珍珠坊所有的客人都赶了出去，因为那些人都太俗，都不配陪你喝酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "最后一坛不是女儿红，真正的女儿红，珍珠坊一共只有三坛。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你喝了六十斤陈酒后，还能分辨出最后一坛酒的真假，真是好酒量。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "是好酒量。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是，今天你却滴酒不沾。是不是知道酒里有毒？你和杜青莲结伴而来，当然知道他在哪里叫的酒菜，要买通一个人在酒里下毒，当然也容易得很。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我已决心宁死不入碧玉山庄，现在杜青莲和沈红叶也死了，碧玉夫人也不必再选，阁下已当然是她东床快婿。这真是可贺可喜。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "我已明白你的意思。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你应该明白。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhen_lin",
      "speaker_name": "金振林",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "邱凤城是我的，这次还轮不到你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhen_lin",
      "speaker_name": "金振林",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "我们还有旧账，旧账一定要先算。今天就是我们算账的时候。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhen_lin",
      "text": "你这个时候选得真巧。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "text": "留下他的活口……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "text": "你说得太迟了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "text": "其实我早就应该想到，你的刀下是从来没有活口的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "绝大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "彭大侠的杀孽虽重，杀的人却都是该杀的人，这人片刻间刀伤五命，死得并不冤枉。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "text": "我只不过想问问他，'聚丰楼'的那五个堂倌和小厮，既非江湖中人，跟他也不会有什么仇恨，他为什么一定要将他们置之死地？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "text": "现在他虽然死了，这件事我们迟早还是问得出的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "text": "问谁？这件事除了他之外，还有谁知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道！这件事幸好还有我知道。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这杆枪并不重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "text": "他练的是家传梨花枪，走的本来是轻灵一路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "据说有人曾经试过，把七个铜钱从他面前抛出去，他一枪刺出，绝对可以把七个钱眼全都刺穿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "text": "他出手的确极准。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "他自己一定也想不到，这次居然会失手。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "text": "这次他也没有失手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "既然他没有失手，你为什么没有死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "text": "这是小婉送给我的，她要我贴身藏着，她要我不要因为别人而忘了她。我没有忘记她，所以我还活着。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来一个人痴情也有好处。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "邱公子，我虽然不认得你，你这对银枪，我却是认得的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "text": "这是晚辈家传之物，晚辈并不敢以此自炫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "我知道。昔年令尊以这对银枪力战'长白群熊'时，我也在场。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "text": "前辈莫非是冯大侠！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "不错，我就是冯超凡。你看见了他刚才那一刀，想必也该知道他是谁了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人一定是作恶多端，才会遇见了五虎断门刀。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "刚才出手的若是这和尚，他死得只怕更快。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_jue_da_shi",
      "text": "这位前辈莫非是少林的绝大师？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "不错，他就是绝和尚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来应该已经死在金振林的枪下，你们三位本来却不该到这里来的，所以这个人的计划本来应该已完全成功，而且永远没有人能揭破他的阴谋和秘密，碧玉夫人不必再费心挑选，这个人已当然是碧玉山庄的东床快婿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到苍天竟将三位前辈送到这里来了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "可是我们本来的确不该来的，也不会来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们本来只不过想到聚丰楼去喝杯酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三杯下肚，我们这三个老头子也动了豪气，想到寒梅谷看看这位雅人。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到我们走到半路，就看见小顾他们的尸身。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "每个人都是一刀就已致命，杀得好干净，好利落！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "text": "他也是用刀，当然更忍不住来看看是谁有这么快的一把刀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_tian_ba",
      "speaker_name": "彭天霸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我们这三个不该来的人就来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "天纲恢恢，疏而不漏，杀人者死！这三句话，你以后一定要牢记在心，千万不要忘记。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 345
    }
  ],
